text: Adrianne Palicki (born May 6, 1983) is an American actress. She was born in Toledo, Ohio. Palicki has acted in both television series and movies. She was in the television series Friday Night Lights (2006–2011) and Agents of S.H.I.E.L.D. (2014–2016). She acted in Legion (2010), Red Dawn (2012), G.I. Joe: Retaliation (2013), and John Wick (2014). == References == Category:Actors from Toledo, Ohio Category:American movie actors Category:American television actors Category:1983 births Category:Living people
